---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Koleksi Buku Anak Digital">
  <section class="max-w-5xl mx-auto py-12 px-4">
    <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold text-pink-700 mb-4 text-center">Koleksi Buku Anak Digital</h1>
    <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-10 text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto">Cerita anak, buku edukasi, dan komik digital untuk menumbuhkan minat baca sejak dini. Semua koleksi dapat diakses gratis dan legal untuk anak-anak Indonesia.</p>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <!-- Contoh Buku Cerita Anak -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg p-6 flex flex-col items-center hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-300 border-b-4 border-pink-400">
        <img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/iniedu/assets/buku-anak-cerita.jpg" alt="Cerita Anak" class="w-28 h-40 object-cover rounded shadow mb-4" />
        <div class="font-bold text-pink-700 mb-2 text-center">Cerita Anak: Si Kancil dan Buaya</div>
        <div class="text-gray-600 text-sm mb-3 text-center">Dongeng Nusantara klasik penuh pesan moral</div>
        <a href="https://drive.google.com/file/d/1l-EXAMPLE/view" target="_blank" class="px-4 py-2 rounded-full bg-pink-500 text-white font-semibold shadow hover:bg-pink-600 transition">Baca Buku</a>
      </div>
      <!-- Contoh Buku Edukasi Anak -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg p-6 flex flex-col items-center hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-300 border-b-4 border-purple-400">
        <img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/iniedu/assets/buku-anak-edukasi.jpg" alt="Buku Edukasi Anak" class="w-28 h-40 object-cover rounded shadow mb-4" />
        <div class="font-bold text-purple-700 mb-2 text-center">Buku Edukasi: Aku Suka Membaca</div>
        <div class="text-gray-600 text-sm mb-3 text-center">Buku latihan membaca untuk anak usia dini</div>
        <a href="https://drive.google.com/file/d/1m-EXAMPLE/view" target="_blank" class="px-4 py-2 rounded-full bg-purple-500 text-white font-semibold shadow hover:bg-purple-600 transition">Baca Buku</a>
      </div>
      <!-- Contoh Komik Anak -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg p-6 flex flex-col items-center hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-300 border-b-4 border-fuchsia-400">
        <img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/iniedu/assets/buku-anak-komik.jpg" alt="Komik Anak" class="w-28 h-40 object-cover rounded shadow mb-4" />
        <div class="font-bold text-fuchsia-700 mb-2 text-center">Komik Anak: Petualangan Si Riko</div>
        <div class="text-gray-600 text-sm mb-3 text-center">Komik edukasi ringan dan menghibur</div>
        <a href="https://drive.google.com/file/d/1n-EXAMPLE/view" target="_blank" class="px-4 py-2 rounded-full bg-fuchsia-500 text-white font-semibold shadow hover:bg-fuchsia-600 transition">Baca Buku</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="text-center text-sm text-gray-500 mt-10">* Semua buku diambil dari sumber legal dan dapat diakses secara gratis.</div>
  </section>
</Layout>
